text: Muhammad Aji Kurniawan (born July 1, 2000) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a winger for Liga 1 club PSM Makassar. ==Career== ===PSM Makassar=== He was signed for PSM Makassar to played in Liga 1. == References == ==External links== * Aji Kurniawan at Liga Indonesia * Aji Kurniawan at Soccerway Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian footballers Category:PSM Makassar players Category:Association football midfielders
